syncModel

public static void syncModel(Model model)
Syncs the entire state document with the frontend. This should happen rarely and typically only when so many parts of the model have changed that it makes sense to sync the whole thing. The model gets very large, however, so this is to be avoided.

Parameters:
model - The model to sync.
